n the environment and that similar appraisal is made of existing agro-chemicals.
\par }\pard\plain \qj\nowidctlpar\adjustright \fs20\lang1031 {<#/>}{\fs24\lang2057 These products, he says, are examined under laboratory and field conditions and evaluated in field trials adding that should a product fail any of these tests it is droppe
d from further development.
